<div class="htj-steps-section page-width">
  <div class="htj-steps-flow">

    <div class="htj-step">
      <div class="htj-step__num">01</div>
      <div class="htj-step__card">
        <h3 class="htj-step__title">Book a Come &amp; Try Session</h3>
        <p>Experience our coaching approach first-hand with a free no-obligation trial session. Meet the coaches, try our training methods, and see if we're the right fit.</p>
        <a href="/pages/free-come-and-try" class="htj-step__btn">Register for Come &amp; Try</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="htj-step">
      <div class="htj-step__num">02</div>
      <div class="htj-step__card">
        <h3 class="htj-step__title">Meet and Greet</h3>
        <p>After your trial session you'll have a brief meet and greet with one of our coaches to discuss your goals, experience, and the best training group for your needs.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="htj-step">
      <div class="htj-step__num">03</div>
      <div class="htj-step__card">
        <h3 class="htj-step__title">Complete the Athlete Intake Form</h3>
        <p>If you decide to join, the next step is completing our intake form. This helps us understand your athletic history, goals, and any specific needs.</p>
        <a href="/pages/trial-successful-join-now" class="htj-step__btn">Athlete Intake Form</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="htj-step">
      <div class="htj-step__num">04</div>
      <div class="htj-step__card">
        <h3 class="htj-step__title">Coach Review &amp; Confirmation</h3>
        <p>Our coaching team will review your information and contact you within 3 business days to confirm your placement and provide details about your first regular session.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="htj-step">
      <div class="htj-step__num">05</div>
      <div class="htj-step__card">
        <h3 class="htj-step__title">Optional: Scholarship Application</h3>
        <p>We offer a limited number of scholarships for talented athletes. If this applies to you, you can apply for scholarship consideration.</p>
        <a href="https://forms.office.com/r/33fZRRtCvd" target="_blank" class="htj-step__btn">Scholarship Application</a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .htj-steps-section {
    padding: 0 20px 60px;
  }

  .htj-steps-flow {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .htj-step {
    display: flex;
    align-items: stretch;
    gap: 0;
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background-color: #111111;
  }

  .htj-step__num {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 100px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    color: #82f2b3;
    background-color: #0d0d0d;
    border-right: 4px solid #82f2b3;
    padding: 24px 16px;
  }

  .htj-step__card {
    padding: 28px;
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .htj-step__title {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .htj-step__card p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: #e0e0e0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .htj-step__btn {
    display: inline-block;
    align-self: flex-start;
    background-color: #82f2b3;
    color: #0a2910;
    padding: 12px 22px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 6px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    margin-top: 4px;
    transition: opacity 0.2s ease;
  }

  .htj-step__btn:hover {
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .htj-step {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .htj-step__num {
      width: 100%;
      height: 64px;
      border-right: none;
      border-bottom: 4px solid #82f2b3;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      justify-content: flex-start;
    }

    .htj-step__card {
      padding: 20px;
    }
  }
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "How to Join Steps",
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "How to Join Steps"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
